Anagram Palindrome
Difficulty: BasicAccuracy: 44.28%Submissions: 48K+Points: 1
Given a string s, determine whether its characters can be rearranged to form a palindrome. Return true if it is possible to rearrange the string into a palindrome; otherwise, return false.










class Solution {
public:
    bool canFormPalindrome(string &s) {
        int count[26] = {0};
        for(int i = 0;i<s.length();i++){
            count[s[i]-'a']++;
        }
        int cnt = 0;
        int kcnt = 0;
        for(int i = 0;i<26;i++){
            if(count[i]%2 == 0){
                cnt++;
            }
            else{
                kcnt++;
            }
        }
        if(kcnt > 1){
            return false;
        }
        return true;
    }
};
